data.description: Come see this completely renovated home that is ready to move in! There is new LVT throughout the house and new carpet in the 3 bedrooms upstairs. New kitchen cabinets with self-closing doors and drawers, granite counter tops with a breakfast bar that could have multiple uses, and a backsplash. All black appliances stay with the home. The roof is less than 1 year old, new screen and screen door on the front porch overlooking the beautiful yard with a beautiful tree! Exterior has fresh paint, and a new outside AC unit with the interior unit serviced! This home also has 2 master bedrooms one could be used for an in-law suite, roommate, or you could turn it into a game room or theater! New Ring doorbell and camera flood light have been installed and stay with the home. Come see today!
